title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 12 2021

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1: Cubans are protesting communism in their country by waving the United States flag in their streets. Don’t tell Colin Kaepernick. Clay: If supporting protests in a communist country in favor of freedom and democracy is a “big test” for you, your party is morally bankrupt. Cuban government takes a page out of the authoritarian/tyrant playbook and starts to shut down communications. Cuban-American callers weigh in on the protests.
